description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Hanry performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 10, 2023. 

Songs:
Cavale
Cyclone
Brouillard Asphalte

Matilde Lejas - Bass
